{"tid":2276084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人成日嗌交","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T20:36:09.000Z","uid":217162,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02f28d7e05623760767b2824154ba89d9d1edbe6","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"屋企人事無大小郁啲就嗌交 輕則嘈兩句 重則又話離婚又剩 又打自己咁<br />\n<br />\n老母係果種好鍾意將一件小事無限大嘅人 我老豆又係果種唔識講嘢有時講嘢好撚難聽嘅大男人<br />\n<br />\n夾係中間真係好撚辛苦 叫佢哋唔好成日嗌交 佢哋又話咩唔係嗌交 只係講嘢大聲 三日唔理又嘈過<br />\n<br />\n係好細個嘅時候已經試過係半夜比佢地嗌交嗌到嘈醒左 之後聽到啲掉嘢聲嚇到係到喊郁都唔敢郁<br />\n至此有左心理陰影 佢哋一嗌交我會入房匿埋唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2fae8501f6c9ec20bbcb462a9c23e1ff1f722c","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過佢哋係有精神病？"},{"pid":"21d43127f83ee3570563dc688e2701ce8826c25c","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d2fae8501f6c9ec20bbcb462a9c23e1ff1f722c","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過佢哋係有精神病？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"我思疑我阿媽就黎有 成日小小事都勁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1605fa047abcb8184a90255d514505c5b1804a14","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21d43127f83ee3570563dc688e2701ce8826c25c","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d2fae8501f6c9ec20bbcb462a9c23e1ff1f722c","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過佢哋係有精神病？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"我思疑我阿媽就黎有 成日小小事都勁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"可能係更年期？<br />\n<br />\n其實長期喺咁嘅環境生活，係精神虐待嚟，你應該都冇能力搬出去，實好難頂"},{"pid":"b64f44da271b44343c18388c3b66377460d824cf","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1605fa047abcb8184a90255d514505c5b1804a14","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21d43127f83ee3570563dc688e2701ce8826c25c","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d2fae8501f6c9ec20bbcb462a9c23e1ff1f722c","tid":2276084,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過佢哋係有精神病？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"我思疑我阿媽就黎有 成日小小事都勁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"可能係更年期？<br />\n<br />\n其實長期喺咁嘅環境生活，係精神虐待嚟，你應該都冇能力搬出去，實好難頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"仲讀緊書 <br />\n真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活環境好壓抑<br />\n唔係話我屋企人唔好 只不過係佢哋成日嗌交<br />\n我阿媽郁啲就話離婚 郁啲就話要死 再唔係自殘打自己<br />\n我驚幫佢搵社工搵醫生 又會驚我阿媽覺得自己以為自己有病係痴線 之後又無限放大"},{"pid":"c22b9a20a7d8fdb049ca554d3a8ffe9014c7ca33","tid":2276084,"uid":253984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:23:58.000Z","msg":"絲打同我嘅情況完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b92a7b2b635e241cc17a63c17137152b4da887d","tid":2276084,"uid":217162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c22b9a20a7d8fdb049ca554d3a8ffe9014c7ca33","tid":2276084,"uid":253984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:23:58.000Z","msg":"絲打同我嘅情況完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"我係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣好辛苦 做架兩又會比人屌埋一份"},{"pid":"f7eeb04a2941809b5749f901e457601ecf67a499","tid":2276084,"uid":332769,"l